## About {{ agents.store_name }}

{{ agents.store_name }} is a heritage Bengali sweets (mithai) brand from Kolkata, India, established 1885. We make traditional Bengali sweets and savouries, and festival, wedding and corporate gifting.

- **Key categories:** Sandesh, Rosogolla, Mishti Doi, Nolen Gur sweets, dry-fruit mishti, tin / packed sweets, gift boxes, wedding tattya / dala, and corporate gifting.
- **Currency:** {{ agents.currency }} (India)

